	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Solve the Colony's illithid Vault puzzle (use &quot;oe COL_Vault_AutoSolve&quot;)&#xD;&#xA;- Walk over to the large vault door and interact with the Grand Design sculpture at the ledge&#xD;&#xA;- After that dialog finishes, each user will get this Daisy AD once." />
